    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁刘易斯因美国指控而股价上涨 730%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/billionaire-joe-lewis-nets-730-gain-on-stock-behind-us-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国亿万富翁乔·刘易斯(Joe Lewis)已退出其在一家处于美国内幕交易案件核心的生物技术公司的股份，并于本周认罪，从而巩固了八倍的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/billionaire-joe-lewis-nets-730-gain-on-stock-behind-us-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 18:01:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戴蒙表示富人应该支付更多资金来资助低收入减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/dimon-proposes-cutting-low-income-taxes-even-if-wealthy-pay-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为低收入美国人减税将改善他们的向上流动性、整体健康和生活，并有助于美国经济的增长——即使这样做意味着提高富裕人群的税收，摩根大通和公司首席执行官杰米戴蒙说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/dimon-proposes-cutting-low-income-taxes-even-if-wealthy-pay-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 17:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
